Run without subcommands to open the Bubble Tea scheduler review/apply screen.
Subcommands remain available for non-interactive usage:
  plan status
  plan target add|list|delete|set-active
  plan constraint show|set
  plan generate

Recommended scheduler workflow:
  1) set targets
     pomo plan target add --domain Math --subtopic Discrete --cadence weekly --hours 8
  2) review/update constraints
     pomo plan constraint set --weekdays mon,tue,wed,thu,fri --day-start 08:00 --day-end 22:00 --max-hours-day 8
  3) preview generation
     pomo plan generate --from 2026-03-01T00:00 --to 2026-03-08T00:00 --dry-run
  4) apply generation
     pomo plan generate --from 2026-03-01T00:00 --to 2026-03-08T00:00 --replace

Usage:
  pomo plan [flags]
  pomo plan [command]

Available Commands:
  constraint  manage scheduler constraints
  generate    run balanced scheduler generation for workload targets
  status      show planned vs done counts in a date range
  target      manage workload targets

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for plan

Use "pomo plan [command] --help" for more information about a command.
